 since that time ihs continues to grow both organically and through acquisitions adding additional products and services and expanding the list of industries it serves ihs nyse ihs and markit nasdaq mrkt announced the signing of a definitive agreement under which the companies combined an allshare merger of equals to create a global leader in critical information analytics and solutions on march   based on the closing prices of ihs and markit common stock on march   the implied equity value of the transaction was valued at more than  billion upon completion of the merger the combined company was renamed ihs markit and the headquarters moved from englewood colorado to london uk however certain key operations are still based in englewood colorado supported industries and business processesedit ihs provides products and services in the following industries aerospace defense and security automotive chemical economics  country risk energy finance maritime and trade technology media  telecom healthcare  pharmaceuticals  products and servicesedit ihs offers four broad categories of products and services industry data and analyses technical documents custom software applications consulting services and industry expertise industry informationedit ihs analyzes and distributes information on aerospace defense and security automotive chemical economics  country risk energy finance maritime  trade technology healthcare  pharmaceuticals to customers in more than  countries technical documentsedit ihs distributes technical documents such as domestic and international standards developed by standards development organizations sdos such as the telecommunications industry association astm international astm esdu now owned by ihs and the institute of electrical and electronics engineers ieee regulatory guideline information and documentation including restriction of hazardous substances directive rohs and waste electrical and electronic equipment weee custom software applicationsedit ihs develops custom software applications that integrate ihs information databases with their clients’ inhouse management software applications such as enterprise resource planning erp product lifecycle management plm consulting servicesedit ihs provides consulting services across a wide array of industries including aerospace defense and security automotive chemical economics  country risk energy finance maritime  trade technology healthcare  pharmaceuticals drawing on expertise from acquired companies such as cera jane’s herold isuppli global insight polk carfax joc and fairplay acquisitionsedit ihs has embarked on an aggressive acquisition program in the last several years acquiring the following companies among others caps computer assisted product selection electronics component database of partminer  information handling service purchases petroconsultants s a out of geneve switzerland this acquisition was the first of many acquisitions to provide ihs with the detailed exploraiton and production databases petroconsultants s a was approximately  employees providing details on the worlds oil and gas wells fields basins surveys licensing economics legal fiscal and contractual terms for e and p activity globally  information handling service purchases pidwights this purchase provided the full united states data coverage providing well and production data this formed a division called ihs energy group  information handling service purchases mai consultants who provided quetor software and databases to provide detailed costs data for activity around the world  information handling service purchased ieds a uk based company that had a detailed far east database and research as well as emerging research in other regions around the world their research and leadership were leveraged in the emerging global integration of research by combined companies  information handling service purchases petroleum data services which provided detailed log services to the usa data compilation this provided much more deep data within north america  ihs purchases accumapenerdata which provides the detailed canadian exploration and production databases  ihs purchases international petrodata ltd providing canadian well bore data  ihs purchases imonitoring from luna innovations which provided real time monitoring of production using cellular technologies this was later resold to another entity ferguson beauregard  ihs purchases geofluids data and software from rakhit petroleum consulting  ihs purchases cera – cambridge energy research associates a company founded by pulitzer price author dan yergin  ihs purchases central marketing and advantage programs which provided canadian seismic data details  ihs purchases canadian hydrodynamics which provided dst research  ihs purchases geoplus the company that had petra software for doing geologic interpretations  ihs purchases nixon digital data logs which provides log data for south texas  ihs purchases john s herold who has detailed information on the valuation strategy and performance of over  public ally traded companies as well as the most comprehensive transaction database covering the upstream exploration and production  ihs purchases three north american companies providing interpreted well top information which provides the most comprehensive database of interpreted tops companies purchased included exploration data services gcs and gds  ihs purchases rapidata which provided detailed canadian well test pressure and completion data  ihs purchases sdg oil and gas a boutique consulting group  ihs purchases global insight the worlds largest economics organization serving over  clients in industry finance and government worldwide with revenues of over  million in  and employing more than  economists and other staff in  offices in  countries – ihs purchases janes information group a global information provider to the aerospace and aerodefense industries and to government agencies janes publishes the renowned